metadata.name: Birth
metadata.description:
“Birth” marks the beginning of this collection which is a personal journey on its own.

Being nude in an extremely challenging environment, pushing through the discomfort only with the trust I have in myself and the clarity of my vision. This mirrors a time when I needed to cancel out the outside world while I was unable to hide who I was. Taking steps towards the light, towards unknown freedom and self-love.
I learnt to stay authentic and strong in my vulnerability.

The outcome is beautiful, the pain was worth it.
